<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-a-row">in a row</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>排成一排；连续地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The children were asked to stand in a row. 
孩子们被要求站成一列。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve beaten the record three times in a row. 
我已经连续三次打破这一记录了。</p></div></div>